grade_evaluation.et:
Final score of the subject (total 100 points) shall be composed as followings:

1) Participation in compulsory seminars (4 seminars may provide in total 12 points);
- Participation in marked 4 seminars is compulsory;
- In every compulsory seminar the student may collect maximum 3 points for the active participation (participation in the discussions);
- Participation in the compulsory seminars towards obtaining the points involves active participation and engagement in the discussions;

2) Legal memo assignment provides maximum of 13 points;

3) Final exam in subject: max 75 points.

4) Additional 3 points for participation in legal clinic (if celebrated)
